Sentencas: With recent progress in lowering the operating temperature, chromia-forming ferritic stainless steels are considered as promising interconnect materials for solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: Magnetron-sputtered Mn/Co(40:60) coating on ferritic stainless steel SUS430 for solid oxide fuel cell interconnect applications

Sentencas: To block the chromium evaporation and chromium poisoning, coatings with Mn/ Co (40:60) was tested as the optimized recipe to maintain Mn1.5Co1.5O4 composition after long term operation due to Mn diffusion from substrate.
Titulo: Magnetron-sputtered Mn/Co(40:60) coating on ferritic stainless steel SUS430 for solid oxide fuel cell interconnect applications

Sentencas: In order to study the coating thickness effect, Mn/Co (40:60) coatings were fabricated in thickness of approximately 800 nm, 1500 nm, 3000 nm on ferritic stainless steels SUS430 using magnetron sputtering.
Titulo: Magnetron-sputtered Mn/Co(40:60) coating on ferritic stainless steel SUS430 for solid oxide fuel cell interconnect applications

Sentencas: Oxidation behavior of sputtered samples was investigated after oxidized at 800 degrees C in air for 2 h, 250 h, 500 h, 1000 h, respectively.
Titulo: Magnetron-sputtered Mn/Co(40:60) coating on ferritic stainless steel SUS430 for solid oxide fuel cell interconnect applications

Sentencas: SEM, EDS, XRD and FIB are used to analyze the surface morphology, chemical composition and structures of the coatings.
Titulo: Magnetron-sputtered Mn/Co(40:60) coating on ferritic stainless steel SUS430 for solid oxide fuel cell interconnect applications

Sentencas: Area specific resistance measurement indicated the sputtered samples in thickness of 800 nm, 1500 nm, 3000 nm at 800 degrees C for various hours in air are in range of 15-36 m Omega cm(2), 12-25 m Omega cm(2), 10 23 m Omega cm(2) respectively.
Titulo: Magnetron-sputtered Mn/Co(40:60) coating on ferritic stainless steel SUS430 for solid oxide fuel cell interconnect applications

Sentencas: Eventually the optimized thickness of Mn/Co (40:60) coatings was suggested.
Titulo: Magnetron-sputtered Mn/Co(40:60) coating on ferritic stainless steel SUS430 for solid oxide fuel cell interconnect applications
